metadata.title: L.O.L. Surprise! Jacket and Tutu Dress for Girls Sizes 4-16
features: ✔ FUN FASHION: L.O.L. Surprise! girls apparel outfit bundle set comes to life with fun vibrant printed colors, sparkling with glitter, printed sleeve on the LOL Surprise bomber jacket and tulle skirt tutu dress. This colorful graphic printed jacket is made of 100% polyester fabric. The short sleeve L.O.L. Surprise graphic tutu dress is made of 100% cotton jersey material and the tulle skirt is made of 100% polyester.

✔ FAVORITE CHARACTER: Let your little one represent their favorite L.O.L. Surprise! characters whether they are part of the Glitterati, Art, Atheltic or any of the other LOL Surprise clubs. With all the glitz & glam this L.O.L. Surprise! graphic jacket & tutu dress is great for any L.O.L. Surprise! fan who wants to wear L.O.L. Surprise! clothes.
✔ OFFICIALLY LICENSED: 100% Officially licensed L.O.L. Surprise! apparel product makes the perfect gift for every child and premium quality you expect & deserve from L.O.L. Surprise! clothing.
✔ MULTIPLE SIZES: Choose from little girls 4-6 range or big girls 7-16 range from XS-4/5, SM-6/6x, MD-7/8, LG-10/12, XL-14/16.
✔ OCCASIONS: Great for Birthdays, Christmas, Gift Giving, Back to School, or Just general everyday use.
description: Let your child represent L.O.L. Surprise! in this adorable fashionable sporty comfortable L.O.L. Surprise bomber jacket & all over print tulle skirt tutu dress.
